```python id=golden
import numpy as np

N = 4  # 2^n_sys, n_sys = 2
i = np.arange(N).reshape(N, 1)
j = np.arange(N).reshape(1, N)
golden = np.exp(2j * np.pi * (i * j) / N) / np.sqrt(N)  # shape (4,4), analytic DFT
golden = golden.astype(complex)
```
